  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a small-scale shooting game that is very casual and easy to play. You need to find 3 controllers in an abandoned warehouse and successfully activate them to pass the level. When you activate the controller, there will be a steady stream of zombies to stop you. You must protect the controller while defeating the zombies. The game fails when the health bar reaches 0. Every time you defeat a zombie, it will drop supplies, some of which can increase bullets and health.</p>",
